Uses of Package
com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel

  • Packages that use com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel 
    Package Description
    com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel
    The streetlevel package provides classes, interfaces, and enumerations that display an interactive StreetLevelFragment.
  • Classes in com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel used by com.here.android.mpa.streetlevel 
    Class and Description
    StreetLevel
    Represents a street level object at a particular geographic location.
    StreetLevelBillboard
    Represents a street level billboard object.
    StreetLevelBillboardOrientation
    Encapsulates the orientation for StreetLevelBillboard) objects that users can add to a StreetLevelModel.
    StreetLevelBillboardOrientation.Orientation
    This enumeration defines values for billboard orientation options
    StreetLevelBuilding
    Represents all street level building objects that are a visible component of an on-screen StreetLevelFragment.
    StreetLevelCoverage.Listener
    Represents a listener to provide notification upon completion of a StreetLevelCoverage operation.
    StreetLevelCoverage.ResultCode
    Represents values describing possible result types of the coverage check operation
    StreetLevelGesture
    Encapsulates all user interactions and gestures that are applicable to a StreetLevelFragment.
    StreetLevelGesture.OnGestureListener
    Event Listener interface for gesture events.
    StreetLevelIcon
    Represents a class for all street-level icon objects.
    StreetLevelIconBase
    Represents a base class for all image-based street level objects that users can add to a StreetLevelModel.
    StreetLevelIconPlacement
    Encapsulates the placement properties for all image-based street-level objects (StreetLevelIcon or StreetLevelBillboard) that users can add to a StreetLevelModel.
    StreetLevelIconPlacement.HorizontalPlacement
    This enumeration defines values for automatic placement in lat/long coordinates.
    StreetLevelIconPlacement.VerticalPlacement
    This enumeration defines values for automatic placement in altitude.
    StreetLevelIconSize
    Encapsulates the size properties for a StreetLevelIcon.
    StreetLevelIconSize.ScalePolicy
    Represents values describing the policy for scaling a StreetLevelIconSize.
    StreetLevelModel
    Represents a model for street level data.
    StreetLevelModel.OnEventListener
    Represents a listener to provide notification upon completion of a StreetLevelModel event.
    StreetLevelModel.OnRetrievalListener
    Listener class to be used with StreetLevelModel.getStreetLevel(GeoCoordinate, StreetLevelModel.OnRetrievalListener) to retrieve a StreetLevel.
    StreetLevelModelState
    Represents a composite class comprising the zoom level, heading, pitch and roll for a StreetLevelModel.
    StreetLevelObject
    Represents a base class for all street level related objects that users can add to an on-screen StreetLevelModel instance.
    StreetLevelObject.Type
    Represents values describing the types of objects that a user can add to a StreetLevelModel instance by calling StreetLevelModel.addStreetLevelObject(StreetLevelObject).
    StreetLevelOffScreenCapture
    StreetLevel derivation of the com.here.android.mpa.common.OffScreenRenderer renderer.
    StreetLevelProxyObject
    Represents a base class for all street level objects rendered as part of the map.
    StreetLevelProxyObject.Type
    Represents values describing the types of objects that can be retrieved from a StreetLevelModel instance by calling StreetLevelModel.getSelectedObjects(PointF).
    StreetLevelRoute
    Represents a route displayed within a StreetLevelFragment
    StreetLevelSelectedObject
    Represents a base class for all objects that are selectable on a StreetLevelFragment.
